1. . ___________________[NAME] hereby elects to satisfy his/her tax withholding obligation arising upon the vesting of the [restricted stock/restricted stock unit] by having Apple withhold that number of shares with a fair market value equal to the minimum amount required to be withheld under applicable tax laws.
