3.      Indenture; Defined Terms.
This Note is one of the 3.85% Notes due 2043 (the "") issued under an indenture dated as of April 29, 2013 (the "") by and between the Issuer and the Trustee, as supplemented by an Officer's Certificate dated May 3, 2013, issued pursuant to Section 301 of the Indenture (together with the Base Indenture, the ""). This Note is a "Security" and the Notes are "Securities" under the Indenture.
